name: QWERTY: Into madness
description: After multiple months of slacking off and multiple redesigns I bring to you... QWERTY: Into madness! This is the biggest wad I've ever made! Having a total of ten jaw dropping maps! This wad will leave you in pure bliss at the magnificence of this wad. Inspired from the works of Nambona890, DrewPicklesOgre, Marvin "OneTrueCyber" Moore, Joey, Terry, Steelen and multiple other excellent Doomers! Also sv_infiniteammo 1 IS recommended for this wad.
